Cell C has launched a new data promotion for Black Friday, offering SmartData Share plans which feature triple the data. The operator’s SmartData Share 5GB, 10GB, 20GB, and 50GB plans will now offer triple the amount of Anytime and Nite data for any customers who sign up for these SIM-only deals. Qualifying customers will receive the promotional data for the duration of the 24-month contract. “Our SmartData Share plans are already packed with fantastic value, offering customers a generous allocation of anytime and nite data,” said Cell C Chief Commercial Officer Junaid Munshi. “As a summer special, we have further boosted the anytime and nite data on these plans, essentially giving you triple the value.” “Customers will be hard pressed to find a better data deal in the market,” he said. SmartData Share plans also provide customers with up to 1,000 free Wi-Fi calling minutes and customers can link up to 14 SIMs. These promotion deals are detailed below, and are available until 6 January 2018.